downloadDescription: The IA-32 Execution Layer is a software driver designed to improve performance of 32-bit applications running on Windows Server 2003 for 64-bit Itanium-based Systems.
detailsSection: The IA-32 Execution Layer is a software driver designed to improve performance of 32-bit applications running on Windows Server 2003 for 64-bit Itanium-based Systems.
systemRequirementsSection: Any Itanium 2-based system that is running one of the supported operating systems.
